author: tellison
msg: Refactoring and fixing more networking code
- remove createSocket() call, now use either createStreamSocket() or createDatagramSocket()
- remove SocketImplProvider, and in-line the few static methods it had
- remove PlainServerSocketImpl, it is sufficient to use PlainSocketImpl
- remove PlainSocketImpl2, it is sufficient to use PlainSocketImpl
- fix bug in NIO SocketChannelImpl to map Inet ANY address to Localhost on connect request
- workaround bug in NIO SocketChannelImpl that flips non-blocking socket to blocking during finishConnect
